                            help users discover income opportunities, including
                            but not limited to:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Income finder and recommendation tools</li>
                            <li>Educational blog articles</li>
                            <li>Resource guides and recommendations</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h2>3. User Responsibilities</h2>
