                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                That our recommendations will lead to specific
                                income levels
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of
                                information
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                That the website will be available at all times
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            Income results vary based on individual effort,
                            skills, market conditions, and other factors beyond
                            our control.
                        </p>

                        <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                        <p>
                            SideBuzCom shall not be liable for any direct,
                            indirect, incidental, special, or consequential
                            damages resulting from your use of our website,
