                            logos, and software, is the property of SideBuzCom
                            and is protected by copyright laws. You may not
                            reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works
                            without our written permission.
                        </p>

                        <h2>8. Modifications to Terms</h2>
                        <p>
                            We reserve the right to modify these Terms of
                            Service at any time. Changes will be effective
                            immediately upon posting to the website. Your
                            continued use of the website after changes
                            constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
